{"id":113650,"type":2,"name":"Steamboat Willie","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/38/2e/113650_guw55.jpg","rating":{"total":83,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":2,"5":2,"6":9,"7":36,"8":23,"9":4,"10":7},"score":7.4},"summary":"《汽船威利号》（Steamboat Willie）是华特迪士尼全球第一出有声的动画片，动画片的主角是著名的米奇老鼠。此影片于1928年11月18日在纽约79街殖民大戏院（Colony Theater）上映，米老鼠的生日便定为了那天。\r\n\r\n片内的米老鼠没有说话，只随着轻快的音乐跃动和吹口哨。其形象博得观众的喜欢，并轰动了全纽约。随即米老鼠就成了举世闻名的“明星”。1932年，这部影片更获得了奥斯卡的特别奖。 据说上映时，纽约人到场看的并非剧情，而是这只可爱的老鼠，在这八分钟内彻底的娱乐了在座的市民们。\r\n","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>汽船威利号</li><li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>製作: </span><a href=\"/person/6816\">Walt Disney Pictures</a></li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/13956\">Walt Disney Animation Studios</a></li><li><span>上映年度: </span>1928-11-18</li><li><span>片长: </span>8分钟</li><li><span>导演: </span>Walt Disney / Ub Iwerks</li>","collection":{"wish":13,"collect":131,"on_hold":5,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"短片","count":39},{"name":"Disney","count":31},{"name":"欧美","count":27},{"name":"1928","count":26},{"name":"迪士尼","count":18},{"name":"美国","count":11},{"name":"米老鼠","count":10},{"name":"考古","count":9},{"name":"奥斯卡","count":8},{"name":"原创","count":7},{"name":"万恶之源","count":6},{"name":"先驱","count":4},{"name":"始祖","count":3},{"name":"剧场版","count":3},{"name":"UbIwerks","count":2},{"name":"短篇","count":2},{"name":"20年代","count":1},{"name":"1928年11月","count":1},{"name":"Short_film","count":1},{"name":"1900-1949","count":1},{"name":"系列短片","count":1},{"name":"动画","count":1},{"name":"【ANIME】短片丨美国","count":1},{"name":"WaltDisney","count":1},{"name":"Walt","count":1},{"name":"搞笑","count":1},{"name":"动画短片","count":1},{"name":"欢乐","count":1},{"name":"美国动画","count":1},{"name":"Walt.Disney.Pictures","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":856403,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/856403","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":6816,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4f/85/6816_prsn_MGpfY.jpg","name":"迪士尼电影公司","desc":"製作"},{"id":13956,